title: Damn Demonic Swords
description: Damn Demonic Swords Manhwa Signature Jagger is a warrior who lives with the creed, ‘Pay back gratitude two fold, resentment ten fold!’ actively avoiding troublesome matters. Unsure if it’s coincidence or inevitable, he is followed around by demonic swords who have turned into young girls by getting into all sorts of twists and turns… Warrior of doom Signature Jagger, if you can’t avoid it, then slay everything in the path! Damned Cursed Swords, Cursed Demonic Swords, The Demon Swords of Condemnation, The Magic Swords of Damnation, 빌어먹을 마검들
